Package: rcol
Type: Package
Title: Catalogue of Life Plus Client
Description: Client for the Catalogue of Life Plus ('CoL+') webservice 
    (<https://github.com/CatalogueOfLife/general>). The CoL+ webservice is
    a new interface to the Catalogue of Life. Includes functions for each
    of the API methods, including searching for names, and more.
